[log] bash[80] stdout **Parameter Description**:
[log] bash[80] stdout - `alpha` (float): The viewing angle parameter of the camera, used for distance calculation
[log] bash[80] stdout - `v0` (float): The vertical offset parameter of the camera intrinsic matrix
[log] bash[80] stdout - `ay` (float): The focal length parameter of the camera intrinsic matrix
