[log] bash[80] stdout ### Node 7: Hardware Control Interface
[log] bash[80] stdout **Function Description**: Control the hardware devices of the RC car through serial communication, achieving precise motion control. Support multiple control instructions and real-time response.
[log] bash[80] stdout **Core Algorithms**:
[log] bash[80] stdout - Serial communication protocol
[log] bash[80] stdout - Control instruction encoding
