[log] bash[80] stdout ```python
[log] bash[80] stdout class RCControl(object):
[log] bash[80] stdout     def __init__(self, serial_port):
[log] bash[80] stdout         self.serial_port = serial.Serial(serial_port, 115200, timeout=1)
[log] bash[80] stdout     def steer(self, prediction):
[log] bash[80] stdout         if prediction == 2:
[log] bash[80] stdout             self.serial_port.write(chr(1).encode())
[log] bash[80] stdout             print("Forward")
[log] bash[80] stdout         elif prediction == 0:
[log] bash[80] stdout             self.serial_port.write(chr(7).encode())
[log] bash[80] stdout             print("Left")
[log] bash[80] stdout         elif prediction == 1:
[log] bash[80] stdout             self.serial_port.write(chr(6).encode())
[log] bash[80] stdout             print("Right")
[log] bash[80] stdout         else:
[log] bash[80] stdout             self.stop()
[log] bash[80] stdout     def stop(self):
[log] bash[80] stdout         self.serial_port.write(chr(0).encode())
[log] bash[80] stdout ```
[log] bash[80] stdout **Control Command Mapping**:
[log] bash[80] stdout - `prediction == 0`: Left turn (send `chr(7)`)
[log] bash[80] stdout - `prediction == 1`: Right turn (send `chr(6)`)
[log] bash[80] stdout - `prediction == 2`: Forward (send `chr(1)`)
[log] bash[80] stdout - Other: Stop (send `chr(0)`)
