[log] bash[163] stdout     def evaluate(self, X: np.ndarray, y: np.ndarray) -> float:
[log] bash[163] stdout         """
[log] bash[163] stdout         Evaluate the model accuracy on the provided data.
[log] bash[163] stdout         Parameters:
