[log] bash[1073] stdout class DistanceToCamera:
[log] bash[1073] stdout     """Calculate the distance from a detected object to the camera.
[log] bash[1073] stdout     Uses camera intrinsic parameters and triangulation to compute
[log] bash[1073] stdout     real-world distance in centimetres from the image-plane y
[log] bash[1073] stdout     coordinate of the target base.
