[log] bash[1643] stdout class RCControl:
[log] bash[1643] stdout     """
[log] bash[1643] stdout     Control the movement of the RC car through the serial port.
[log] bash[1643] stdout     Control Command Mapping:
[log] bash[1643] stdout         prediction == 0: Left turn  (send chr(7))
[log] bash[1643] stdout         prediction == 1: Right turn (send chr(6))
[log] bash[1643] stdout         prediction == 2: Forward    (send chr(1))
[log] bash[1643] stdout         other:            Stop       (send chr(0))
[log] bash[1643] stdout     """
[log] bash[1643] stdout     def __init__(self, serial_port):
[log] bash[1643] stdout         """
[log] bash[1643] stdout         Initialize the RC car controller.
[log] bash[1643] stdout         Args:
